的小女孩（蛮可爱的），并罚她在神社乾活，弥补飞船撞坏神社的过失。\r\n　　可是，一但秋菜灵力减弱时，海多拉的封印就会消失，不死心的海多拉又会想出什么办法来对付瓦尔古雷呢？　　 ","date":"2002-07-04","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/6d/e4/4383_jZUlF.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/6d/e4/4383_jZUlF.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/6d/e4/4383_jZUlF.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/6d/e4/4383_jZUlF.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/6d/e4/4383_jZUlF.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":5462,"total":188,"score":6.3,"count":{"1":0,"2":2,"3":2,"4":3,"5":35,"6":63,"7":58,"8":19,"9":4,"10":2}},"tags":[{"name":"TV","count":79},{"name":"2002","count":39},{"name":"圆盘皇女","count":36},{"name":"漫画改","count":35},{"name":"瓦尔Q蕾","count":28},{"name":"卖肉作","count":28},{"name":"漫改","count":26},{"name":"TNK","count":24},{"name":"后宫","count":24},{"name":"2002年","count":21},{"name":"卖肉","count":20}],"eps":12,"collection":{"wish":346,"collect":324,"doing":43,"on_hold":56,"dropped":35}},{"id":12786,"type":2,"name":"朝霧の巫女","name_cn":"朝雾的巫女","summary":"稗田家三姐妹，长女仓子、次女柚子及幼女珠，她们作为稻生神社的巫女，为了保护身为审神者后裔的天津忠寻，同时也为阻止妖魔入侵校园，而组织了“巫女委员会”。 朝雾的巫女等级与一般巫女不同，能自由自在地操纵包含阴阳道在内的各种咒语，可说是巫女中的巫女。而审神者则是负责将神灵凭依在适当的媒介上，并判别神明与妖魔的人，忠寻因为是审神者后裔，有着召唤强大神灵的力量。整个故事就在正邪的对抗中展开……","date":"2002-07-04","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/5d/ac/12786_Iji2d.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/5d/ac/12786_Iji2d.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/5d/ac/12786_Iji2d.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/5d/ac/12786_Iji2d.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/5d/ac/12786_Iji2d.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":7150,"total":70,"score":5.5,"count":{"1":0,"2":2,"3":2,"4":10,"5":20,"6":22,"7":10,"8":3,"9":0,"10":1}},"tags":[{"name":"TV","count":33},{"name":"搞笑","count":21},{"name":"林原惠","count":15},{"name":"2002","count":14},{"name":"2002年7月","count":13},{"name":"堀江由衣","count":12},{"name":"Starchild","count":10},{"name":"漫画改","count":9},{"name":"GANSIS","count":8},{"name":"2004","count":